title: How To Install a K&N Air Intake on a 2005-2014 Toyota Tacoma 4.0L
description:
See how easy it is to install a K&N Air Intake on your 2005 to 2014 Toyota Tacoma 4.0L.

K&N 57-9025 performance air intake system is easy to install and guaranteed to increase horsepower in 2005 to 2014 Toyota Tacoma with a 4.0L engine. When dyno tested, this air intake created an estimated gain of 8.91 horsepower at 4857 RPM.

This air intake includes an oversized washable & reusable air filter that can go up to 100,000 miles between servicing. K&N air intake 57-9025 also includes a custom rotomolded intake tube and aluminum heat shield to isolate intake air from engine heat.  It also maintains use of the factory hydrocarbon trap.
